@SG_CPP_CLASS SGRElementBufferObject
@SG_SHORT_DESCRP GPU side element buffer object
@SG_LONG_DESCRP SGRElementBufferObject is used by @SG_FINDREP_RENDERER renderers to store element buffer objects on the GPU.
@SG_IMPLE @SG_FINDREP_RENDERER internally uses QRhi.
@SG_FUNC SGRElementBufferObject(SGRBaseRenderer* renderControl, int bufferSize);
Creates a SGRElementBufferObject with a size of $bufferSize bytes associated to the @SG_FINDREP_RENDERER renderer $renderControl.
@SG_WARN Negative $bufferSize is undefined behaviour.
@SG_WARN Passing nullptr to $renderControl is undefined behaviour.
